\title{Generalized PROs}
\taxon{theory}
\import{macros}

\p{The \define{theory of generalized PROs} is the [theory of unnormalized
PROs](thy-000P) augmented with the \em{normalization axiom}: the unit cell
#{\theta} is a restriction, i.e., the unique globular cell

#{\id_x \To m(\eta_x, \eta_x)}

factoring #{\theta} through any chosen restriction is an isomorphism.}
